@startuml
autonumber
skinparam DefaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor Client
participant "REST API\n(Controller)" as API
participant "Service Layer\n(Service + AOP)" as Service
participant "Persistence\n(jOOQ)" as Repo
database "Database" as DB
participant "Audit\n(JaVers)" as JaVers

== Erfolgsfall (Success) ==
Client -> API: PUT /sensors/1\n(JSON inkl. Version 1)
API -> Service: update(sensorDto)
Service -> Repo: save(domainSensor)
Repo -> DB: UPDATE sensors SET ..., version = 2\nWHERE id = 1 AND version = 1
DB --> Repo: 1 row affected
Repo --> Service: savedSensor (Version 2)
Service --> API: success
Service -> JaVers: AOP @AfterReturning:\ncommit(savedSensor)
API --> Client: 200 OK

== Fehlerfall (Optimistic Lock Failure) ==
Client -> API: PUT /sensors/1\n(JSON inkl. Version 1)
API -> Service: update(sensorDto)
Service -> Repo: save(domainSensor)

note over Repo, DB: Ein anderer Prozess hat die DB-Zeile\nzuvor bereits auf Version 2 aktualisiert!

Repo -> DB: UPDATE sensors SET ..., version = 2\nWHERE id = 1 AND version = 1
DB --> Repo: 0 rows affected
Repo --> Service: DataChangedException
note right of Service: Transaktion wird\nzurückgerollt (@Transactional)
Service --> API: Exception geworfen
note over Service, JaVers: AOP-Aspekt feuert NICHT.\nEs wird kein Audit-Eintrag erstellt!
API --> Client: 409 Conflict (bzw. via @ExceptionHandler)
@enduml